<br>
&quot;Father! I was afraid you would miss the beloved event.&quot;<br>
<br>
She kissed her father on the cheek gently looking at him with a daughter's admiration that none of the others granted him.<br>
<br>
She cast a slight glance to Hera and smiled to her step-mother.<br>
<br>
